    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and grate <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red onion</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1682353689669-x200.jpg",
