            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> to a separate bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Once the sweet potato fries are almost done, add your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s] </strong>to the tray[s] and return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
