        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb is cooked, remove from the oven and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Transfer the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>lamb</strong> to a clean board and slice into long strips – this is your <strong>lamb doner meat</strong></p>",
