    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>warmed pitta</strong> with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>lamb doner meat</strong>, <strong>onion slices</strong> and <strong>tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Drizzle over some of the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>and <strong>chilli sauce </strong>and serve the <strong>sweet potato fries</strong> and <strong>remaining garlic mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
